Sentencas: The purpose of this work was to study the transient performance of solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) under several cycling conditions, in order to understand the degradation mechanisms.
Titulo: Cycling studies of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Initially, the Rolls Royce Fuel Cell IP-SOFC (Integrated Planar SOFC) single tube was investigated.
Titulo: Cycling studies of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The objective was to cycle up to 100 times to check if degradation was occurring and to assess its extent.
Titulo: Cycling studies of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this paper the results of loading cycles at nominally constant operating temperature are reported.
Titulo: Cycling studies of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Work on two other kinds of cycles, i.e. thermal and redox, for this type of tube has commenced and the results will be reported in the follow-up paper.
